title: Rage.of.The.Battlemage.MULTi5-PROPHET
description:
Rage of the Battlemage (c) dev4play

release date: August 2769
protection: # of discs: 1
languages: EN/ES/PL/RU/TR

Rage of the Battlemage is a dynamic hack'n'slash
game, where you take control over Lorthan, the last
living battlemage in the world covered in darkness
evil and brutality. Your goal is to defend those
taken by demons vast lands and send their generals
straight to hell. You will be forced to learn how
demons fight, how to take terrain to your adventage
and upgrade your skills. Save all the lands
forests, ice lands and even volcanic terrain and
more, where evil grows strong. Remember to watch
out for deadly traps. Face many kind of enemies
deadly bosses and dive into the rage of the
Battlemage!

1- Unpack, burn or mount
2- Install the game
3- Copy the cracked content from PROPHET dir
4- Go To Hell!
